      "text": [
        "٣٦٢. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): مَنْ ضَنَّ بِعِرْضِهِ فَلْيَدَعِ الْمِرَاءَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "362. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: He who is jealous of his esteem should keep from quarrelling."
